description:
What role has Jesuit education played in Satans war strategies against Christ and His people? Have strategies in Sun Tzus Art of War been employed against Protestantism? What was the purpose of the creation of the Jesuit Order and how have the Jesuits used learning against learning to bring the world back under Romes control? How do the military orders of the Roman Catholic Church operate? And what has this got to do with Gnosticism and its entrance into the church? 

The Jesuit Order was ousted from most European nations in the 18th century and was finally banned by the Pope himself in 1773, only to be reinstated in 1814. What happened there? Might Sun Tzus  Art of War shed some light on this subject? 

The Art of War is credited to Chinese military strategist Sun Tzu who is said to have written the book in the 5th century BC. It was translated by a French Jesuit in 1772. According to this book, all warfare is based on deception. Was the suppression of the Jesuits a strategy of deception? What have the Jesuits accomplished since that period in their history? While the world has been distracted by false flags, has the enemy already taken the field?

Satan has studied humanity for millennia, and he knows how to tempt the human heart. He has acquired an army that does his bidding. We need to understand the ongoing battle so we can better guard and prepare ourselves. Military orders such as the Knights of Malta and the Jesuits are in positions of great power and influence. What are they accomplishing through events we hear about in the news? What are their plans? Will they succeed? 

Discover more: https://amazingdsicoveries.org
